2 sa eva ānandamayaḥ darpaṇaḥ, aham ca āsvemi sma,
3 madhureṇa tiktaṃ samāpaynaṃ kṛtvā;

19 Jayantī mama hasitamālokya,
20 uvāca mama: "Parivartaya śṛṇu ca;
21 na kevalam mama netradvaye svargaḥ asti."

37 Aham adṛkṣam kṛṣāya pravartitam jyotir
38 Iṣu-nāmadheyena, yathā sa cakāra;
39 Na ca mayā jñātam āsīt nāma tat karmaṇaḥ pūrvam.

52 Aham mama dakṣiṇa pakṣāt apavartate
53 Beatricies tatra mama kartavyaṃ draṣṭum,
54 vācā vā ceṣṭayā vā sūcitaṃ;

79 Prathamaṃ, gāyantaḥ, svayaṃ notāya calantaḥ;
80 tataḥ, eṣām ekaṃ lakṣaṇaṃ bhavataḥ,
81 alpam kālaṃ tiṣṭhanti smaunaḥ.

91 ‘NYĀYAM PREMATA’, ādyam
92 sarvasya citrasya kriyā-nāmadheyau āstām;
93 ‘YŪYAM PṚTHIVĪM VIṢAHATHA’, āsanāni āsan.

103 tatra sahastrādhikāḥ jyotirmaṇḍalāni punaḥ sambhūtāni dṛṣṭāni,
104 cañcalāni ca, anyāni ca sthairāṇi,
105 yathā sūryaḥ tāni prakāśayati;

109 Yaḥ tatra citram ālikhati, na tasya ko 'pi netā asti;
110 kim tu sa svayam eva netā asti, tataś ca sa smaratī
111 tām śaktim, yā nidānāṃ nimitta-rūpam asti.

118 Tasmāt aham prārthayāmi tam manas, yasmin prārambhase
119 tava gatiḥ ca tava śaktiś ca, yathā paśyet
120 kutaḥ nirgacchati sa dhūmaḥ yaḥ tava raśmimācchādayati;

127 Pūrvam khadgena saha yuddhaṃ kriyate sma;
128 api tu adhunā kriyate apaharataḥ atra atra ca
129 annam yat kṛpāluḥ pitā na ke'pi niṣedhati.
